herical object</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 161, 188)\">cutting</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">through the sky past your home. Descending rapidly at a vertical arch,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 161, 188)\">speeding</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">past your home until…</span><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 11, 11)\">THOOM!</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 0, 201)\">imminent</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">sound of the object crashing deep in the</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 201, 0)\">forestry</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">parts of a rural area, causing nestled birds to scatter and leaving a thick stream of ashy smoke in its wake. Having</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 161, 188)\">driven</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">there in your (Your choice), you watched your footing as you gaze down the rather deep</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 201, 0)\">crater</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">after the dust settled, you sighted the </span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 41, 118)\">spherical object</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> which had turned out to be some form of foreign</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217)\"> </span><span style=\"color